<ul>
  <li>Explainable AI for ML models</li>
  <li>The next of Graph Neural Networks (or Network Embedding)</li>
  <li>Commonsense reasoning for the next of QnA system</li>
  <li>Federated Learning on Inter-connected data</li>
  <li>ML models for Sensor Systems (EMG/EEG)</li>
  <li>(You can also suggest any new topic!)</li>
</ul>

